# Book Management System

## How to Run
### Backend (ASP.NET)
1. Navigate to `BookApi` folder.
2. Run `dotnet run` or open in Visual Studio and press F5.
3. API runs on: `https://localhost:7103` (Update your Angular service if different).

### Frontend (Angular)
1. Navigate to `book-management` folder.
2. Run `npm install`.
3. Run `ng serve`.
4. Open browser at `http://localhost:4200`.
